The paper proposes a new method for recommender systems that combines deep learning and collaborative filtering. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper utilizes auxiliary information and content-based features, which are common in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) research. Finally, the paper evaluates its method on real-world datasets, which suggests that it may also belong to the Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) sub-category.
